attributionInfo.brokerName: Coldwell Banker Sea Coast Advantage - Jacksonville

data.description: Southern Style 3 bedroom 2 bath Ranch. Featuring open floor plan!  Vaulted ceiling in Living room/dining room.  Nine foot ceilings in other areas. 1800 Sq. Ft. Split bedroom plan.  Featuring large laundry/utility room with washer/dryer and utility sink.  An additional space near kitchen and garage with mini-split -- use as home office.  Double garage with separate doors /door openers.  Beautiful wood floors throughout.  Tiled kitchen and bathrooms. Also featuring a large rear deck that opens off dining and kitchen area. Includes  Hook Up for RV. Also an Amazon BLINK SYSTEM. Community is a short distance toBeaufort for great dining and shopping, to Atlantic Beach for Sun bathing and swimming and other areas of Harkers Island and Down East for easy access to the open waters and public boat ramps.  Cape Lookout National Seashore close by. Sellers say bring an offer!
